This project's authentication flow (src/auth/**) and HTML parsing approach
(src/parsing/**) are a TypeScript port of design and logic from the Python
project "amazon-orders" by Alex Laird:

    https://github.com/alexdlaird/amazon-orders

That project is used under the MIT License, reproduced below. No code from
that project is directly included (this is an independent TypeScript
implementation), but the login state machine, CSS selectors, and page-parsing
approach are derived from reading its source, so its license terms are
included here per the MIT License's attribution requirement.

